            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                In <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>onorem</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>omus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ivinae</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>sanct</abbr><ex>ae</ex></expan> Dia<lb break="no" n="3"/>nae aram <lb n="4"/>cum signo Ae<lb break="no" n="5"/>tetus <expan><abbr>Aug<am>g</am></abbr><ex>ustorum</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>ostrorum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>lib</abbr><ex>ertus</ex></expan> p<expan><ex>rae</ex><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ositus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>stat</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> Ma<lb break="no" n="7"/><expan><abbr>iens</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> XXXX <expan><abbr>Gall</abbr><ex>iarum</ex></expan> de<lb break="no" n="8"/><expan><abbr>dic</abbr><ex>avit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Id</abbr><ex>ibus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Praesent</abbr><ex>e</ex></expan> co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ule</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Datierung: entweder 217 oder 246. Auf der linken Nebenseite urceus, auf der rechten Nebenseite patera. Hederae als Worttrenner in Z. 2. Aus Platzmangel zahlreiche Buchstaben im unteren Teil der Inschrift klein ausgeführt Z. 6: A; MA-Ligatur; Z. 7: E in D eingeschrieben; Z. 8: A, S, N, OS. (B): Außerhofer: Z. 8: Praesent(e) I c(onsule).</p>
            </div>
